Cou'd play Towns in Fingaul.

               Portlaughrin, and Towns in Fingaul.

               Bunratty;

And 

Pars ingenti ſubiere Pharetro.
                mounted him upon a Beer;

               Mac-Murreartagh 


Terribili ſqualore Charon.

               O Cha-roon;



Eripe me his invicte malis, aut tu mihi Terram 

Injice—
                To throw my Carcaſs in a hole;



Nullae ſic inſidiae tales abſiſte moveri. 

Nec vim Tela ferunt.
                Hold, hold! My Ears thou'rt after grateing;

And ſhall diffuſe it's Vertue here;

Huc geminas inflecte acirs, hanc aſpice gentem 

Romanoſque tuos.—
